  "texts": [
    "introduced textrank [13], an algorithm that uses several statistical features and one specialized function that calculates a weighted sum for calculating the similarity between sentences [14].",
    "Query based text summarizationIn this technique, the summaries are generated by a scoring mechanism.",
    "The sentences that contain the query terms are scored higher and thus obtain higher ranks.",
    "These highranked sentences constitute the summary of the input documents.",
    "More specifically, this approach centres around the user query terms and their extensions."
  ]
